# APIFaultRadar - Outage & Error Spike Monitor

APIFaultRadar watches multiple endpoints and flags abnormal latency, timeouts, or HTTP errors in bursts.

## Features
- Spike and fault detection  
- Realtime scan loop  
- CSV/JSON reporting

## Usage
```bash
git clone https://github.com/your-username/32_APIFaultRadar.git
cd 32_APIFaultRadar
python monitor.py
